{"tid":1781336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[出書啦] 中信圍困日記開始預售","createTime":"2019-12-13T05:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T03:48:33.000Z","uid":230609,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc7a8f4d30905ecd1affb79979f00200d694f35","tid":1781336,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"「人與政權的鬥爭，就是記憶與遺忘的鬥爭」- 米蘭&middot;昆德拉<br />\n我們說香港人善忘，是因為太多應該被銘記的，卻終究被我們遺忘<br />\n當街頭上的連儂牆被拆去、樓梯間的遺書被刷掉、直播的片段被剪走，這場運動尚未完結，運動的痕跡卻已經被掩蓋<br />\n612，這場運動最原初的夢，大規模警暴的開端，應該刻劃於香港人共同歷史上的一天<br />\n你，會遺忘嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我哋收集咗超過30個親歷者嘅紀錄，以日記形式，編錄成實體書，還原真相，書寫我哋共同嘅歷史。<br />\n目前呢本書嘅內容已經完成，而家進行緊預售，有興趣買嘅可以入嚟睇下詳情，預售收入扣除成本會捐晒畀立場新聞同埋 誌hk.feature：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/6-12-中信圍困事件受訪紀錄/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F6-12-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E5%9C%8D%E5%9B%B0%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%2F&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6pdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=4b64d7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/6-12-中信圍困事件受訪紀錄/</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果訪問：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190704/59788377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190704%2F59788377&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6pdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=23b18b2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190704%2F59788377&h=cdf26196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190704/59788377</a><br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇議員訪問花絮：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=PfDik6j_8HM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPfDik6j_8HM&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6pdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=f3d9e876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=PfDik6j_8HM</a><br />\n<br />\n_________________________________________________________________________<br />\n書本內容節錄：<br />\n//我呆著看著他旁邊的人，不停往他身上倒生理鹽水，好像在救火一樣，那畫⾯我畢⽣難忘。 //<br />\n<br />\n//我在這裏衷心感謝室內的人，他們不斷幫忙拉人進去，疏散人群。無論情況多麼嚴峻，都沒有人踩人，大家依然在危難中互相扶持。//<br />\n<br />\n//突然，身旁響起「砰」的一聲巨響。直覺是黑警連在建築物內的人也不放過？當下有一名先生立刻叫大家伏在地上，喊著不要讓警察看見我們。 //<br />\n<br />\n//轉眼以後，前方已經滿佈全套裝備的警察，但是我們也沒能看得清楚，舉傘，人鏈，靜下。有人忽然開口問：「退到這邊安全嗎？」「這裏現在已經是前線！前後都是前線了！」//<br />\n<br />\n//寫這段字，我全身都在震，知道網上在傳當天的片段，自己也不敢看。佛說要對別人慈悲，但這刻我沒辦法對殺人政權慈悲；我願有天自己能對他們慈悲。//"},{"pid":"b3387501811977ebcdc5500d30b55b5720a37f3a","tid":1781336,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:40:45.000Z","msg":"預售詳情link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/6-12-中信圍困事件受訪紀錄/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F6-12-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E5%9C%8D%E5%9B%B0%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%2F&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6pdwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=4b64d7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/6-12-中信圍困事件受訪紀錄/</a>"},{"pid":"c8c68157e962ab1b373b779e811971bc5179e5b4","tid":1781336,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875986fe6982eb52e8f136a393acfe2760728b8c","tid":1781336,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166aa1229b6ae0d29ca0936d70c3f3fe4b732147","tid":1781336,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7f78b78b50a0b7e5be2c7256ee56e09a54067b","tid":1781336,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T05:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\